<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1流式响应与业务事务冲突">问题1：流式响应与业务事务冲突</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：流式输出期间数据库连接未释放
<strong>解决</strong>：在调用AI前完成所有数据查询，或调整连接池配置</p>]]></description></item><item><title>Spring AI 架构原理与底层实现</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/ai%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/spring-ai%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/ai%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/spring-ai%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="spring-ai-架构原理与底层实现">Spring AI 架构原理与底层实现</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Spring AI 通过 <code>Model</code> + <code>Prompt</code> + <code>OutputParser</code> 三层抽象统一了不同大模型供应商的 API 差异，底层基于 <code>RestClient</code> 和 <code>ReactiveChatClient</code> 实现同步/流式双模调用，其设计本质是<strong>将 AI 能力转换为 Spring 生态中可装配的标准 Bean</strong>。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="spring-ai-通过分层架构解耦了模型协议调用方式与业务逻辑">Spring AI 通过分层架构解耦了模型协议、调用方式与业务逻辑</h2>
<h3 id="整体架构五层模型设计">整体架构：五层模型设计</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  应用层：业务代码调用 ChatClient / EmbeddingClient            │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  API层：Prompt、ChatResponse、Generation 等通用模型           │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  客户端层：ChatClient / StreamingChatClient 接口抽象          │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  模型层：OpenAiChatModel / AnthropicChatModel / Ollama...    │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│  传输层：RestClient (同步) / WebClient (响应式流式)            │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>层级</th>
          <th>职责</th>
          <th>核心接口/类</th>
          <th>设计意图</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>应用层</td>
          <td>业务编排</td>
          <td><code>ChatClient</code>, <code>Advisor</code></td>
          <td>链式调用、AOP扩展</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>API层</td>
          <td>协议无关的数据结构</td>
          <td><code>Prompt</code>, <code>Message</code>, <code>ChatResponse</code></td>
          <td>屏蔽供应商差异</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>客户端层</td>
          <td>调用模式抽象</td>
          <td><code>ChatClient</code>, <code>StreamingChatClient</code></td>
          <td>统一同步/流式入口</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>模型层</td>
          <td>供应商具体实现</td>
          <td><code>OpenAiChatModel</code>, <code>AnthropicChatModel</code></td>
          <td>协议转换、鉴权、序列化</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>传输层</td>
          <td>HTTP通信</td>
          <td><code>RestClient</code>, <code>WebClient</code></td>
          <td>复用 Spring 6 HTTP 基础设施</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="与-spring-生态的集成点">与 Spring 生态的集成点</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// Spring Boot 自动配置：只需引入 starter，注入即可用</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@Autowired</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">private</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ChatClient</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">chatClient</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 默认指向 spring.ai.default.chat 配置的模型</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 多模型配置：同时对接 OpenAI 和本地 Ollama</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@Autowired</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@Qualifier</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;openAiChatClient&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">private</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ChatClient</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">openAiClient</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@Autowired</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@Qualifier</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;ollamaChatClient&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">private</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ChatClient</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">localClient</span><span class="p">;</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-yaml">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c"># application.yml 多模型配置</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">spring</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
